topic.title: Supported Electrical Interfaces and Clients

body.p: The table below provides a summary of the supported electrical interfaces and client protocols for each SERDES interface. Refer to the RAPTR specification 1 for the electrical specifications for each SERDES type.

table.title: DIGI-G5 Supported Electrical Interfaces and Client Protocols

row.entry: 24x P56 SERDES w/ RX AC-coupling caps

li.p: C2C is Chip-to-Chip; C2M is Chip-to-Module
The P56 Serdes transmitter is MR compliant, while the receiver is MR compliant if driven by a LR compliant transmitter or if the channel is less than 14dB
Nokia Interface only available on Serdes Bank B [23:0] and Serdes Bank C [7:0]
